df = pd.read_csv("AppleMobility.csv")
df2 = pd.read_csv("1_owid/owid-covid-data.csv")

visited=[]

for x in df['region'][0:154]:
  if not x in visited:
    print(x)
    visited.append(x)
    countrymob = df.loc[df['region'] == x]
    countrymob= countrymob.T
    countrymob=countrymob.drop(['geo_type','region','sub-region','country','transportation_type','alternative_name'])
    countrymob = countrymob.T.reset_index(drop=True).T
    countrymob["total"]=0
    for j in range(0, len(countrymob.columns)-1):
      countrymob["total"] = countrymob["total"]+countrymob[j]
    rel=100*(len(countrymob.columns)-1)
    countrymob["total"]= (countrymob["total"]-rel)/100
    countrymob.index.name = 'dates'
    countrymob.reset_index(inplace=True)
    countrymob['dates'] = pd.to_datetime(countrymob['dates'])
    countrycases = df2.loc[df2['location'] == x]
    x = pd.to_datetime(countrycases['date'])
    plt.plot(countrymob.iloc[:,0], countrymob['total'], label="Total Apple London Mobility")
    plt.plot(x, (countrycases['reproduction_rate']-1), label="Reproduction Rate")
    plt.ylabel("Cases")
    plt.title("Cases vs. Mobility")
    plt.legend()
    plt.show()
